videos.description: Jarrett Stidham runs it in from 15 yards out for Auburn's first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Stidham 15-yard TD

videos.description: Darius Slayton takes the screen pass from Jarrett Stidham 50 yards to set up an Auburn touchdown.
videos.headline: Slayton takes screen 50 yards

videos.description: Cole Kelley gets sacked by Jeremiah Dinson for a loss of 8 yards.
videos.headline: Dinson sacks Kelley

videos.description: Eli Stove takes the reverse 45 yards to get Auburn into Arkansas territory.
videos.headline: Stove takes reverse 45 yards

videos.description: Kerryon Johnson tries to leap over the line to pick up first down but is stopped short.
videos.headline: Arkansas stuffs Johnson on 4th down

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham has his pass intercepted by Kevin Richardson II.
videos.headline: Richardson picks off Stidham

videos.description: Henre' Toliver muffs a punt that is recovered by Auburn's Darrell Williams.
videos.headline: Auburn recovers muffed punt

videos.description: Kerryon Johnson takes the third-down pitch into the end zone for an Auburn touchdown.
videos.headline: Johnson 2-yard TD

videos.description: Gus Malzahn says his up-tempo offense has helped the offense early in the game.
videos.headline: Malzahn says tempo is key to 1st half lead

videos.description: Kamryn Pettway pounds it in from 2-yards out for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Pettway punches in TD

videos.description: Kamryn Pettway goes untouched on his way to a 38-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Pettway breaks off 38-yard TD

videos.description: Ryan Davis takes the pitch on a reverse and throws to Darius Slayton for 62-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Davis throws TD to Slayton on trick play

videos.description: De'Vion Warren takes the kickoff back 100-yards for an Arkansas touchdown.
videos.headline: Warren 100-yard TD return

videos.description: Kamryn Pettway takes the hand off 11-yards for his third touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Pettway runs for 3rd TD

videos.description: Malik Willis flips the ball to Devan Barret who runs it in for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Barrett scores 4-yard TD

videos.description: Auburn defensive lineman Jeff Holland's off season martial arts training helps his pass rushing abilities.
videos.headline: Martial arts helping Holland's pass rush

videos.description: Wide receiver Ryan Davis talks about throwing his first touchdown pass at the college level.
videos.headline: Davis on his first collegiate TD pass
